    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30 minutes of hard work have passed, and it's  finally time for a well-deserved break!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your objective is simple: brew some delicious coffee with the stuff your crew stored inside your spaceship. A task rather simple if you squeeze your brain and think about it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It would be terrible, however, if your colleague connected the <strong>wrong red button</strong> to the USA <strong>nuclear arsenal launch sequence</strong> and your daughter is joyfully going to school, <strong>completely unaware of it<br></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras/a6d070fcacc9e0094af3b461e1e6d637.avif?t=1738764678\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras_big/a6d070fcacc9e0094af3b461e1e6d637.avif?t=1738764678 width=800 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax in the chill atmosphere of deep space, while playing this short-and-sweet <strong>Point and Click Puzzle</strong> game: you only need your dominant hand (or hook, if you are a space pirate) and a mouse to navigate through the playful systems of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself, here are some of them:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> 11 Bad Endings are hidden, for you to avoid them!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Lots of hints</strong> are scattered as <strong>notes and other secrets</strong>, for you to find them!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Franco.</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Epic Interactions:</strong> grab and toss around the items your crew left around in the spaceship, with custom sounds and properties</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Revolutionary <strong>liquids mixing system</strong> (source: trust me, bro).</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Original <strong>Radio Stations</strong>, <strong>achievements</strong> and much more!</i> <br> <br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras/808b11fe4da04054be54fa6eeea4b1b1.avif?t=1738764678\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras_big/808b11fe4da04054be54fa6eeea4b1b1.avif?t=1738764678 width=800 height=240 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Other cool features included:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Real time text translation from Russian</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cool space squids</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Betrayals, tears and drama</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>64% accurate solar system representation</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;More moons in Earth's orbit&quot; FREE DLC</i> <br><strong> </strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras/e0988511db19a7459f7772ab1a560f89.avif?t=1738764678\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275870/extras_big/e0988511db19a7459f7772ab1a560f89.avif?t=1738764678 width=800 height=240 /></span> &quot;Coffee Break was first developed by the craziest AIV students during the Virtualverse, a Game Jam where the top game development schools of Italy battle to the Death for fame and glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was a tough clash, but Coffee Break came out as the winner, bringing home three of the available five prizes, including best game overall.&quot;</p></li></ul>",
